      <title>聯準會希望將資產負債表縮減速度減半</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/fed-officials-preparing-slow-pace-balance-sheet-runoff-2024-04-10/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[聯準會正準備在短期內放慢從資產負債表中剝離國債的速度，政策制定者普遍傾向於將近期的步伐削減約一半，以努力延長減持進程並降低市場風險麻煩。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/fed-officials-preparing-slow-pace-balance-sheet-runoff-2024-04-10/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 18:34:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
